fi.hiit.util

Class DataBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.hiit.util.DataBundle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public final class DataBundle
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A mapping from String values to various types. In effect, a glorified HashMap.
